<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.6.6">
<l>mallarai yaṭṭu māḷak kañcaṉai malaintu koṉṟu</l>
<l>pallara cavintu vīḻap pāratap pōrmu ṭittāy</l>
<l>nallaraṇ kāviṉ nīḻal naṟaikamaḻ nāṅkai mēya</l>
<l>kallaraṇ kāva ḷantaṇ pāṭiyāy kaḷaika ṇīyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who, having [once] subdued wrestlers so that they died,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] having fought and killed Kaṁsa,</l>
<l>Ended the Bhārata War so that many kings fell, perishing,</l>
<l>You of the cool hamlet of stone-walled Kāvaḷam who dwells in Nāṅkai</l>
<l>Within whose fine walls, in the shade of groves, fragrances waft,</l>
<l rend="indent">only you are [our] refuge.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
